OL,3,CPolice crush over 100 vehicles as
OL,4,Cforce cracks down on illegal e-scooter
OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,FMore than 100 vehicles have been
OL,8,Fcrushed by Hampshire Police, as the
OL,9,Fforce cracks down on the illegal use
OL,10,Fof e-scooters and e-motorbikes.
OL,12,FThe campaign 'Operation Crush' is
OL,13,Ffocused on removing vehicles involved
OL,14,Fin crime or used by riders under the
OL,15,Finfluence of drink or drugs.
OL,17,FGovernment figures show that in 2023,
OL,18,F6 people died in e-scooter collisions
OL,19,Fand 416 people were seriously injured
OL,20,Fin e-scooter collisions.
