OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,F105 vehicles were seized last year,
OL,8,Fwhich is almost 70 more than the year
OL,9,Fbefore.
OL,11,FHampshire Police says its 'tougher
OL,12,Fstance' is helping to keep roads safer.
OL,14,FThe Hampshire and Isle of Wight Police
OL,15,Fand Crime Commissioner, Donna Jones,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The police have told me that in
OL,17,Fevery single case of these bikes that
OL,18,Fhave been stopped and seized, they
OL,19,Fhave been directly used for
OL,20,Fcriminality - so transporting drugs
OL,21,Faround, people carrying knives.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
