OL,3,CPolice crush over 100 vehicles as
OL,4,Cforce cracks down on illegal e-scooter
OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,F"These bikes are worth upwards of
OL,8,F#5,000 if you buy them brand new, so
OL,9,Flet's make no bones about this.
OL,11,F"These are criminals who are using
OL,12,Fthese as assets of part of their
OL,13,Fcriminal business and the police have
OL,14,Fa duty to seize them and we will get
OL,15,Fthem crushed."
OL,17,FAlthough the public can buy e-scooters
OL,18,Flegitimately, it is still illegal to
OL,19,Fride the vehicles on public roads.
