OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,FRental schemes in Southampton,
OL,8,FPortsmouth, The Isle of Wight, Poole
OL,9,Fand Bournemouth are available to those
OL,10,Fwith a driving license, but private
OL,11,Fownership is growing.
OL,13,FThe force says they will use their
OL,14,Fdiscretion when stopping offenders who
OL,15,Fcan be fined and given points on their
OL,16,Flicense. They say seizing them is a
OL,17,Flast resort, but they're happy to do
OL,18,Fit.
