OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,FSgt Jamie Dobson, said: "If you are
OL,8,Fusing these things for criminal use,
OL,9,Fif you are using them dangerously on
OL,10,Four roads or if you are causing anti-
OL,11,Fsocial behaviour.
OL,13,F"We will take it off of you and we
OL,14,Fwill look to crush it and prevent you
OL,15,Ffrom having it back so that you can't
OL,16,Fcontinue with this sort of behaviour."
